    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i've been feeling so sick for days and i can't even work like this... i looked online and some people said a single dose shouldn't really do anything to the baby. if i just take one pill right now to get through the night, is that really going to be a big deal? i just need to stop the pressure in my face so i can rest.",
