    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i hear you. i'll try to call my clinic in the morning. but in the meantime, i have some cipro (ciprofloxacin) left over from a different infection i had last year. would that be safer to take for this sinus pressure instead since it's an antibiotic? i just can't wait until tomorrow to feel better.",
